    "In contrast, AI technology presents significant opportunities like improving nuclear safety, enhancing risk detection and response speeds, and increasing operational efficiency.",
    "These opportunities can be maximized by exploring ways for IAEA regulations to appropriately integrate and leverage AI technology.",
    "The literature balances these challenges and opportunities, establishing important foundations for exploring innovative approaches to regulating AI in the nuclear field.",
